column5: I'll bet the replica mount people are already working on it. Great fish and great story too!
Don't care where ya fish, this is a big walleye.http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/thunde...leye-1.4576422PjShorthorn
AND... He released it ! Great Job !!
Awesome fish! And congratulations to the angler for releasing it.
WOW! Fish of a lifetime...Good Job on releasing it.
Robert Monty is my new angling hero! I wish every angler was that humble and released the big breeders.
Wow! And good for him for releasing it!
Now that is a walleye of a lifetime!
What a great looking fish. The walleye I have seen over 29-30" all looked pretty rough around the edges.
